headline: ONCOR TO RELEASE 2025 RESULTS FEBRUARY 26
summary: Oncor Electric Delivery Company LLC ("Oncor") plans to release its fourth quarter and year end 2025 results on February 26, prior to Sempra's (NYSE: SRE) fourth quarter and year end 2025 results conference call. Oncor's earnings release will be available on Oncor's website, oncor.com.
